http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0914863/</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RDPSw6F.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Kiss Kiss Bang Bang 

A murder mystery brings together a private eye, a struggling actress, and a thief masquerading as an actor.  

http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0373469/</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xeT45FJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The Assassination of Jesse James by the Coward Robert Ford 

Robert Ford, who's idolized Jesse James since childhood, tries hard to join the reforming gang of the Missouri outlaw, but gradually becomes resentful of the bandit leader.

https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0443680/</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gCoG7kw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>City of God 

Two boys growing up in a violent neighborhood of Rio de Janeiro take different paths: one becomes a photographer, the other a drug dealer.  

http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0317248/</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/c7gIaiG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Closer 

