http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0206634/</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/nCgPhaM</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[HangingWithMyGnomies]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Ah, America.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/CTISoIM</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/h6Gaj2C.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Is this what it means to be great?</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/CTISoIM</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ButtBot9900]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Run for your life!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/olWMlZU</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Ddu46BM.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/olWMlZU</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[tlamph]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Career day</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/HDKZCGJ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vXwK4ig.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/HDKZCGJ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[candiedyms]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The Idiots of Imgur: A Mini Dump pt 68</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/cADFkgd</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gcBdmoQ.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hwwDUgY.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hUcjjeR.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/J8ANK3x.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LfxqQJw.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src