idth: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Ea4SVDH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6cIPBa6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ysblrkf.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/skHDSwj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/e0SRz9y.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/RliGMWG</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[adamtots]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The monologue for her super villain backstory</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/vHioCvd</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CoxndKM.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/vHioCvd</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[CitizenK9]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Slow-mo trainwreck incoming</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/FHAwekU</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sRe5v3V.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Follow-up to my last post (https://imgur.com/gallery/BxWFAae).  Thanks for everyone who commented there and sent messages.

I called a lawyer...there's nothing really to do...where I am we have no-fault and community property.  There's nothing to sway custody either way, so will likely be 50/50 or close.

I made an appointment with a therapist, but haven't had it yet.

I'm currently on a family trip for the end of summer and it pretty much sucks.  I knew it would be tough, but it's pretty bad.  Tensions are super high and I'm trying to be there for the kids, but they're acting out because I think they can sense the tensions are high.

I'm going to break it to my wife when I get home from work on Monday.  Going to ask for 3-month trial separation...to re-evaluate our goals and where we are.  I've already looked for rooms to rent around my town.  I can afford that no problem, thankfully.  I've written out a plan for how we should evaluate the 3 months and how we should handle the kids.  I've written down the questions we need to explore.

I don't actually think reconciliation will be possible, and I feel awful for leaving the possibility of hope there.

I'm terrified that my kids won't understand.  I'm terrified that my wife won't understand.  I'm terrified that my family won't understand.  I'm terrified my coworkers and friends won't understand.  I'm terrified that the universe will punish my cruelty.

But I have to do it.  I need to find happiness for myself and my wife needs to find it for herself.

